Take a break &#8212; our next issue is June 7

</b><br></font><font color="black" face="Arial,Sans-serif" size="2">

We publish the Windows Secrets Newsletter weekly, on the 1st through 4th 
Thursdays of each month. We work hard to bring you the best new 
information, but in months that have a 5th Thursday, we take a break that week 
to recharge our batteries and do long-term research. That means you won't see a newsletter on 
May 31. Our next regular issue will appear on June 7. Go outside 
and smell the roses! &#8212;<i>Brian Livingston, Editorial Director</i><br></font>

